###Url
```bash
/questions/<id>
```
###Method
```bash
Delete
```
###Discription
delete question where <id> is the id of required question.
###Response:
```bash
{
  "message": "Deleted",
  "success": true
}
```
###Url
```bash
/questions
```
###Method
```bash
Post
```
###Discription
post a new question,which has a question and answer text,category, and difficulty.
###Data:
```bash
{
      "answer": "Scarab",
      "category": 4,
      "difficulty": 4,
      "id": 23,
      "question": "Which dung beetle was worshipped by the ancient Egyptians?"
    }
```
###Response
```bash
{
  "message": "Inserted",
  "success": true
}
```
##Url
```bash
/questions/search
```
###Method
```bash
Post
```
###Discription
get questions based on a search term (case-insensative).returns any questions for whom the search term is a substring of the question. 
###Data 
```bash
{
	"searchTerm":"which"
}
